        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1827263131" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3768659032591844901">Small masterful piece of fictional work most likely based upon real events and people. About 150 pages of soap opera African politics in the 1960&apos;s that reads like it could be written today. This was near the top of the list of the 75 best books of the last hundred years. It is beautifully written with good detail and use of local dialect. I enjoyed it and would pick up any of the other author&apos;s writings when I run across them. </span>
  <span id="freeText3768659032591844901" style="display:none">Small masterful piece of fictional work most likely based upon real events and people. About 150 pages of soap opera African politics in the 1960's that reads like it could be written today. This was near the top of the list of the 75 best books of the last hundred years. It is beautifully written with good detail and use of local dialect. I enjoyed it and would pick up any of the other author's writings when I run across them. </span>
