<div id="review_3404702370" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3404702370" />
    <a title="qershore" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/75265442-qershore"><img alt="qershore" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1577963597p2/75265442.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3404702370?book_show_action=true">Jun 22, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="qershore" class="user" itemprop="url" name="qershore" href="/user/show/75265442-qershore">qershore</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/75265442-qershore?shelf=read-in-2020">read-in-2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/75265442-qershore?shelf=reviews">reviews</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3404702370" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2153735829839474428">Sadly enough, I don&apos;t know a lot about African culture, politics and struggles beside what is taught in school and university. Through Chinua Achebe&apos;s <i>A Man of the People</i> I gained some knowledge on Nigeria and I&apos;m glad I took so many things from it. <br/>I highly recommend this and can&apos;t wait to read more of Achebe&apos;s work. </span>
  <span id="freeText2153735829839474428" style="display:none">Sadly enough, I don't know a lot about African culture, politics and struggles beside what is taught in school and university. Through Chinua Achebe's <i>A Man of the People</i> I gained some knowledge on Nigeria and I'm glad I took so many things from it. <br />I highly recommend this and can't wait to read more of Achebe's work. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2153735829839474428" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
