<span id="freeTextContainer5146615323796155402">Timeless, gripping and hilarious story, shows us how top guys exploit those below them and flourish even more. They only care about themselves, that&apos;s African politics. All laid out clear in this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText5146615323796155402" style="display:none">Timeless, gripping and hilarious story, shows us how top guys exploit those below them and flourish even more. They only care about themselves, that's African politics. All laid out clear in this book.</span>
